[
  {
    "start": 0.0,
    "end": 18.0,
    "text": "[ Background noise ]"
  },
  {
    "start": 18.0,
    "end": 19.88,
    "text": ">> Are you crazy right there?"
  },
  {
    "start": 19.88,
    "end": 24.24,
    "text": ">> What are you looking at in the red?"
  },
  {
    "start": 24.24,
    "end": 26.4,
    "text": ">> Right now it's kind of open ended."
  },
  {
    "start": 26.4,
    "end": 32.4,
    "text": "I'm kind of putting on business so I can bring the boys into it."
  },
  {
    "start": 32.4,
    "end": 55.4,
    "text": "[ Background noise ]"
  },
  {
    "start": 55.9,
    "end": 58.9,
    "text": ">> Okay Tamila, nice to meet you both."
  },
  {
    "start": 58.9,
    "end": 65.4,
    "text": "[ Background noise ]"
  },
  {
    "start": 65.4,
    "end": 68.9,
    "text": ">> Do you have a budget or something to support your budget for?"
  },
  {
    "start": 68.9,
    "end": 70.9,
    "text": ">> Not really, I'm just shopping."
  },
  {
    "start": 70.9,
    "end": 72.9,
    "text": "I just knew about this apartment."
  },
  {
    "start": 72.9,
    "end": 75.9,
    "text": ">> Do your friends live here?"
  },
  {
    "start": 75.9,
    "end": 78.9,
    "text": ">> No, I was happy."
  },
  {
    "start": 78.9,
    "end": 81.9,
    "text": "I knew about this apartment three years ago."
  },
  {
    "start": 81.9,
    "end": 87.9,
    "text": "[ Background noise ]"
  },
  {
    "start": 87.9,
    "end": 90.9,
    "text": ">> Are you also a highlighted person there?"
  },
  {
    "start": 90.9,
    "end": 91.9,
    "text": ">> Yeah."
  },
  {
    "start": 91.9,
    "end": 97.9,
    "text": ">> I thought that I don't have my ID on me but I didn't bring my ID."
  },
  {
    "start": 97.9,
    "end": 101.9,
    "text": "[ Background noise ]"
  },
  {
    "start": 101.9,
    "end": 104.9,
    "text": ">> If I can give you other things about my LinkedIn."
  },
  {
    "start": 104.9,
    "end": 116.9,
    "text": "[ Background noise ]"
  },
  {
    "start": 116.9,
    "end": 120.4,
    "text": ">> Yeah, I just think I accidentally forgot my wallet."
  },
  {
    "start": 120.4,
    "end": 122.9,
    "text": "If I can give you my passport."
  },
  {
    "start": 122.9,
    "end": 133.9,
    "text": "[ Background noise ]"
  },
  {
    "start": 134.4,
    "end": 137.4,
    "text": ">> When's the latest you move in?"
  },
  {
    "start": 137.4,
    "end": 140.4,
    "text": "[ Background noise ]"
  },
  {
    "start": 140.4,
    "end": 144.4,
    "text": ">> Just so I have an idea of what we might have available."
  },
  {
    "start": 144.4,
    "end": 148.4,
    "text": "[ Background noise ]"
  },
  {
    "start": 148.4,
    "end": 149.9,
    "text": ">> Awesome, thank you."
  },
  {
    "start": 149.9,
    "end": 157.9,
    "text": "[ Background noise ]"
  },
  {
    "start": 157.9,
    "end": 161.4,
    "text": ">> And I don't really have a chance to leave this."
  },
  {
    "start": 161.4,
    "end": 162.4,
    "text": ">> Okay."
  },
  {
    "start": 162.4,
    "end": 164.4,
    "text": ">> It could be sooner or later."
  },
  {
    "start": 164.4,
    "end": 166.4,
    "text": "It depends on what I think."
  },
  {
    "start": 166.4,
    "end": 168.4,
    "text": ">> Yeah, I think we're in it."
  },
  {
    "start": 168.4,
    "end": 169.4,
    "text": ">> Okay."
  },
  {
    "start": 169.4,
    "end": 171.4,
    "text": ">> So we can start here across the hall."
  },
  {
    "start": 171.4,
    "end": 174.4,
    "text": "[ Background noise ]"
  },
  {
    "start": 174.4,
    "end": 175.4,
    "text": ">> Thank you."
  },
  {
    "start": 175.4,
    "end": 176.4,
    "text": ">> Yeah."
  },
  {
    "start": 176.4,
    "end": 178.4,
    "text": ">> Okay, this way here."
  },
  {
    "start": 178.4,
    "end": 180.4,
    "text": "You want to go straight ahead."
  },
  {
    "start": 180.4,
    "end": 182.4,
    "text": "This is our movie theater."
  },
  {
    "start": 182.4,
    "end": 186.4,
    "text": "You can reserve it if you want to use it with just your friends."
  },
  {
    "start": 186.4,
    "end": 187.4,
    "text": ">> Oh, okay."
  },
  {
    "start": 187.4,
    "end": 191.4,
    "text": ">> It is just first come, first serve though, so."
  },
  {
    "start": 191.4,
    "end": 197.4,
    "text": ">> We don't show movies, but it's a smart TV, so it's got all the apps and live TV."
  },
  {
    "start": 197.4,
    "end": 203.4,
    "text": "[ Background noise ]"
  },
  {
    "start": 203.4,
    "end": 207.4,
    "text": ">> And then right here on the left we've got our heat oven."
  },
  {
    "start": 207.4,
    "end": 210.4,
    "text": "So if you work from home, we're going to study."
  },
  {
    "start": 210.4,
    "end": 216.4,
    "text": "And then it's free Wi-Fi and you need to use the seven different tools to serve as well."
  },
  {
    "start": 216.4,
    "end": 217.4,
    "text": ">> Is this 24/7?"
  },
  {
    "start": 217.4,
    "end": 222.4,
    "text": ">> Yep, it is. With a reason, we don't want all our large groups to gather after 10 p.m."
  },
  {
    "start": 222.4,
    "end": 227.4,
    "text": "And then same with the pool, pool and hot tub."
  },
  {
    "start": 227.4,
    "end": 229.4,
    "text": "These aren't actually locked."
  },
  {
    "start": 229.4,
    "end": 231.4,
    "text": "You need your key phone to get in."
  },
  {
    "start": 231.4,
    "end": 237.4,
    "text": "But the pool and the hot tub over there, they're open from Labor Day through Memorial --"
  },
  {
    "start": 237.4,
    "end": 240.4,
    "text": "sorry, Memorial Day through Labor Day."
  },
  {
    "start": 240.4,
    "end": 246.4,
    "text": "And then we've got some grills under the pavilion and a fire pit to the left over there."
  },
  {
    "start": 246.4,
    "end": 251.4,
    "text": "So the outside is always close, 10 p.m. to 7 a.m."
  },
  {
    "start": 251.4,
    "end": 253.4,
    "text": ">> Okay."
  },
  {
    "start": 253.4,
    "end": 260.4,
    "text": ">> And then our regular side has to have coffee station, 20 flowers as well."
  },
  {
    "start": 260.4,
    "end": 266.4,
    "text": "[ Background noise ]"
  },
  {
    "start": 266.4,
    "end": 269.4,
    "text": ">> Do you live in the area right now?"
  },
  {
    "start": 269.4,
    "end": 275.4,
    "text": ">> Kind of. I have an arbor work that I have to meet some people in the office."
  },
  {
    "start": 275.4,
    "end": 276.4,
    "text": "But then I also --"
  },
  {
    "start": 276.4,
    "end": 278.4,
    "text": ">> So you want to be closer to --"
  },
  {
    "start": 278.4,
    "end": 281.4,
    "text": ">> Yeah, maybe. But also I also have like family and sun heights."
  },
  {
    "start": 281.4,
    "end": 284.4,
    "text": ">> Oh, okay. You're like somewhat familiar with the area right now?"
  },
  {
    "start": 284.4,
    "end": 285.4,
    "text": ">> Yes, somewhat."
  },
  {
    "start": 285.4,
    "end": 286.4,
    "text": ">> Some of them."
  },
  {
    "start": 286.4,
    "end": 288.4,
    "text": ">> Not exactly this area, but --"
  },
  {
    "start": 288.4,
    "end": 289.4,
    "text": ">> Yeah, I mean it's a big city."
  },
  {
    "start": 289.4,
    "end": 290.4,
    "text": ">> Yeah, campus, yeah."
  },
  {
    "start": 290.4,
    "end": 293.4,
    "text": "[ Background noise ]"
  },
  {
    "start": 293.4,
    "end": 296.4,
    "text": ">> And some of the theater equipment."
  },
  {
    "start": 296.4,
    "end": 299.4,
    "text": "[ Background noise ]"
  },
  {
    "start": 299.4,
    "end": 301.4,
    "text": ">> And walk through the theater."
  },
  {
    "start": 301.4,
    "end": 306.4,
    "text": "[ Background noise ]"
  },
  {
    "start": 306.4,
    "end": 307.4,
    "text": ">> Thank you."
  },
  {
    "start": 307.4,
    "end": 310.4,
    "text": "[ Background noise ]"
  },
  {
    "start": 310.4,
    "end": 312.4,
    "text": ">> So we can pass it in here a few times a month."
  },
  {
    "start": 312.4,
    "end": 315.4,
    "text": "They're open for anyone to join."
  },
  {
    "start": 315.4,
    "end": 320.4,
    "text": "They're at 6.30 p.m. on the first and third Tuesdays of the month."
  },
  {
    "start": 320.4,
    "end": 321.4,
    "text": ">> Got it."
  },
  {
    "start": 321.4,
    "end": 323.4,
    "text": ">> When your friends and people meet."
  },
  {
    "start": 323.4,
    "end": 324.4,
    "text": "You know they're not today."
  },
  {
    "start": 324.4,
    "end": 328.4,
    "text": "It's like I would say 10 to 15 people to catch on."
  },
  {
    "start": 328.4,
    "end": 329.4,
    "text": "Take care."
  },
  {
    "start": 329.4,
    "end": 332.4,
    "text": "[ Background noise ]"
  },
  {
    "start": 332.4,
    "end": 338.4,
    "text": ">> I'm going to show you one of our one-bedroom's, a pretty standard size and layout."
  },
  {
    "start": 338.4,
    "end": 344.4,
    "text": "In terms of what we have available and what we will have coming available."
  },
  {
    "start": 344.4,
    "end": 349.4,
    "text": "This one is $2,138 a month."
  },
  {
    "start": 349.4,
    "end": 356.4,
    "text": "And it is about 749 square feet per room."
  },
  {
    "start": 356.4,
    "end": 364.4,
    "text": "[ Background noise ]"
  },
  {
    "start": 364.4,
    "end": 368.4,
    "text": ">> We have quite a few different room measures."
  },
  {
    "start": 368.4,
    "end": 370.4,
    "text": "So I just found two people."
  },
  {
    "start": 370.4,
    "end": 374.4,
    "text": "I was going to need you to want pool view."
  },
  {
    "start": 374.4,
    "end": 379.4,
    "text": "And then you tell us what you want and then we hear about from there."
  },
  {
    "start": 379.4,
    "end": 382.4,
    "text": ">> I do like the vibe."
  },
  {
    "start": 382.4,
    "end": 387.4,
    "text": ">> All the places where they are all are one bedroom, see their carpet in your bedroom."
  },
  {
    "start": 387.4,
    "end": 391.4,
    "text": "And then see the floor and your bucket."
  },
  {
    "start": 391.4,
    "end": 394.4,
    "text": "So the tile is back."
  },
  {
    "start": 394.4,
    "end": 398.4,
    "text": ">> What's the standard?"
  },
  {
    "start": 398.4,
    "end": 404.4,
    "text": ">> So one A through one B has a bucket."
  },
  {
    "start": 404.4,
    "end": 408.4,
    "text": "And then the one F through one M do not have a bucket."
  },
  {
    "start": 408.4,
    "end": 411.4,
    "text": "So like I said there's so many different styles in one bed."
  },
  {
    "start": 411.4,
    "end": 416.4,
    "text": "But quite a few of our one bedroom's they do have bucket."
  },
  {
    "start": 416.4,
    "end": 419.4,
    "text": ">> If that's something you like then we would definitely take that into consideration."
  },
  {
    "start": 419.4,
    "end": 421.4,
    "text": ">> All right."
  },
  {
    "start": 421.4,
    "end": 437.4,
    "text": "[ Background noise ]"
  },
  {
    "start": 437.4,
    "end": 441.6,
    "text": ">> So we're going to talk about some issues of the sewer"
  },
  {
    "start": 441.6,
    "end": 443.4,
    "text": "and the general pricing."
  },
  {
    "start": 443.4,
    "end": 447.4,
    "text": "And we are if you're looking to move in like this summer because that's what we decided."
  },
  {
    "start": 447.4,
    "end": 450.4,
    "text": "We do run prep specials."
  },
  {
    "start": 450.4,
    "end": 457.4,
    "text": "So right now if you take possession of a home before June 25th, if you get to nicely,"
  },
  {
    "start": 457.4,
    "end": 460.4,
    "text": "we don't know what we're going to be running in August."
  },
  {
    "start": 460.4,
    "end": 463.4,
